{"lastModified":null,"uri":"c::8346777690::vessel::fe993350-411f-11f0-a4dc-2f733944b44d","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Greece\n\nExperience the pinnacle of maritime luxury with “Aktis,” the Lagoon 42 Catamaran that seamlessly blends style, comfort, and innovation. This catamaran promises an unforgettable sailing adventure, redefining the way you experience the open waters.\n\nElegance and Craftsmanship: From its thoughtfully designed exterior to its meticulously curated interior, “Aktis” is a testament to meticulous craftsmanship. Each detail has been carefully considered to offer a voyage that marries elegance with excitement.\n\nKey Features:\n\nIndulgent Air Conditioning: Stay in your comfort zone regardless of the weather with “Aktis'” integrated air conditioning system. Revel in a consistently pleasant atmosphere that ensures your journey is nothing short of delightful.\n\nSelf-Sufficient Watermaker: Explore uncharted waters confidently, thanks to “Aktis'” cutting-edge watermaker technology. This innovation transforms seawater into a continuous supply of fresh, drinkable water, granting you independence and the freedom to roam.\n\nUninterrupted Power Supply: “Aktis” ensures you’re never without power with its onboard generator. Enjoy uninterrupted access to electricity, enhancing your experience and ensuring all your devices and amenities function flawlessly.\n\nTeak Elegance in the Cockpit: Step into the lap of luxury with the teak-adorned cockpit of “Aktis.” This exquisite detail not only enhances the aesthetics but also provides a comfortable space to relax, socialize, and savor the beauty of the sea.\n\nConclusion: “Aktis” is more than a catamaran; it’s a gateway to a world where luxury, comfort, and adventure converge. Experience the joy of seamless design, cutting-edge technology, and refined living as you embark on a sailing journey that will forever redefine your idea of maritime indulgence.","blueprint":{"name":"AKTIS","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::fe993350-411f-11f0-a4dc-2f733944b44d::assets::1a9efae0-4124-11f0-ba13-1b3b879886bd/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::fe993350-411f-11f0-a4dc-2f733944b44d::assets::6202bca0-4124-11f0-ba13-1b3b879886bd/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::fe993350-411f-11f0-a4dc-2f733944b44d::assets::4b8d39a0-4124-11f0-ba13-1b3b879886bd/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::fe993350-411f-11f0-a4dc-2f733944b44d::assets::f5a3aa10-4123-11f0-ba13-1b3b879886bd/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::fe993350-411f-11f0-a4dc-2f733944b44d::assets::e635c630-4123-11f0-ba13-1b3b879886bd/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::fe993350-411f-11f0-a4dc-2f733944b44d::assets::e6363b60-4123-11f0-ba13-1b3b879886bd/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::fe993350-411f-11f0-a4dc-2f733944b44d::assets::e64137e0-4123-11f0-ba13-1b3b879886bd/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::fe993350-411f-11f0-a4dc-2f733944b44d::assets::e6407490-4123-11f0-ba13-1b3b879886bd/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::fe993350-411f-11f0-a4dc-2f733944b44d::assets::e63e9fd0-4123-11f0-ba13-1b3b879886bd/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::fe993350-411f-11f0-a4dc-2f733944b44d::assets::0d77aba0-4124-11f0-ba13-1b3b879886bd/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::fe993350-411f-11f0-a4dc-2f733944b44d::assets::0d6ef910-4124-11f0-ba13-1b3b879886bd/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::fe993350-411f-11f0-a4dc-2f733944b44d::assets::0d6de7a0-4124-11f0-ba13-1b3b879886bd/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::fe993350-411f-11f0-a4dc-2f733944b44d::assets::273d6b10-4124-11f0-ba13-1b3b879886bd/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::fe993350-411f-11f0-a4dc-2f733944b44d::assets::2747a440-4124-11f0-ba13-1b3b879886bd/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::fe993350-411f-11f0-a4dc-2f733944b44d::assets::2740ed80-4124-11f0-ba13-1b3b879886bd/{imageVariant}","/medi